data.description: Welcome to your new home, rich in history and character, atop the highest point in quaint and charming Bessemer City!  This incredible home is filled with beautiful, original detail along with many modern conveniences.  From the huge rooms, sweeping staircase, secret area behind the bookcase, hardwood floors and original lighting fixtures, to the mountain views from your second-story terrace and 2 screened porches, this home has something to offer everyone.  Sale includes 6 lots with 2 acres in total.  This is a perfect property for your large or growing family and even has a perfect layout for the most beautiful bed and breakfast. Don't forget to check out the adorable downtown area and Holiday lights off 12th street while you're here!
